    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Training (Taijutsu)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> </p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b>  | <b>Perform DC:</b> </p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> None</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Practice makes perfect, especially when aim is involved. With this training, you've worked on the motions of plucking something small and soft from a slight cavity - not very practical. Unless you count, of course, the eyes.<br><br>Normally, making a called shot to the eyes is a -12. This training reduces the penalties by 1 at each odd level of mastery, to extricate an opponent's eye with your bare hands.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> Training (f), Sleight of Hand 10 ranks</p>\n",
